               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
            
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus target="#1a"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1878Marbab">Marbabta Salomon</title>
                     
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ጸሎት፡ በንተ፡ አስማተ፡ ሰሎሞን፡ ዘረከቦሙ፡ ለነሀብት፡ 
                        ወለአጋን<supplied reason="omitted">ን</supplied>ት፡ ከመ፡ መርበብተ፡ አሣ፡ ዘባሕር፡ እንዘ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ይብል፡</supplied> ሱዱቃኤል፡ አደታኤል፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ወዘንተ፡ ሶበ፡ ይቤ፡ ሰሎሞን፡ ጠፍዑ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ሠራዊተ፡ ነሀብት፡ ከመ፡ ጢስ፡ ከማሁ፡ አጥፍኦሙ፡ ለነሀብት፡ ወለአጋንንት፡ እምላዕ<supplied reason="omitted">ለ፡</supplied>
                        <del rend="erasure">ገብርከ፡</del> ዓመትከ፡ አጻብዓ፡ ድንግል፡ <add place="overstrike">ወለተ፡ ዓ<supplied reason="omitted">ቢየ፡</supplied> እግዚእ፡</add> 
                        እስመ፡ አልቦ፡ ነገር፡ ዘይሰአኖ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር።
                     </explicit>
                     <note>
                        The prayer is followed by a short invocation to Solomon, which begins as follows: 
                        <q xml:lang="gez">ኦዘፈታ<supplied reason="omitted">ሕ</supplied>ኮ፡ እሙቃሔ፡ እዱ፡ ወእግሩ፡</q>. 
                        The name of the first owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11702AsabeaDe">ʾAṣābǝʿa Dǝngǝl</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the end of the 
                        text and replaced with that of <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11701WalattaAE">Walatta ʿAbiya ʾƎgziʾ</persName>.
                     </note>
                  </msItem> 
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus target="#1b"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4692MagicPr">Ṣalot baʾǝnta fǝtḥata śǝrāy za-kin wa-za-ṭǝbab</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ጸሎተ፡ ፍትሐተ፡ ሥራይ፡ ዘተወድሐ፡ 
                        
                           <sic>እም፸፩፡</sic>
                         መጻሕፍት፡ ወወፅአ፡ እምኤሩሳሌም፡ ወዘሠአሮሙ፡ ለመሠርያ<supplied reason="lost">ን፡</supplied>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ይትሰአር፡ ሥራያቲሆሙ፡ ወአስማቲሆሙ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይቅረቡ፡ ኀበ፡ ነፍሱ፡ ወሥጋሁ፡ <add place="overstrike">ወለተ፡ ዓቢ<supplied reason="omitted">የ፡</supplied> ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡</add>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>
                        The name of the owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11701WalattaAE">Walatta ʿAbiya ʾƎgziʾ</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula at 
                        the end of the text. The name of Kidāna Māryām (possibly the same as <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11698KidanaMa">Kidāna Māryām</persName>) is written over erasure.
                     </note>
                  </msItem> 
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus target="#1b"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4704MagicPr">Ṣalot baʾǝnta māʿśǝromu la-ʾagānǝnt</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ማዕስሮሙ፡ ለአጋንንት፡ አህያ፡ ሸራህያ፡ አልሻዳይ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ዘ<supplied reason="omitted">በ</supplied>መስቀልከ፡ አጽራዕከ፡ ግብሮ፡ ለዲያብሎስ፡ ከማሁ፡ አፅርዕ፡ ወአእት<supplied reason="omitted">ት</supplied>፡ ሥራየ፡ 
                        ዓመ<add place="interlinear">ት</add>ከ፡ አጻብዓ፡ ድንግል፡ <add place="interlinear">ወለተ፡ ዓቢየ፡ እግዚእ፡</add>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>
                        The name of the first owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11702AsabeaDe">ʾAṣābǝʿa Dǝngǝl</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the end of the 
                        text. The name of a later owner, <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11701WalattaAE">Walatta ʿAbiya ʾƎgziʾ</persName>, is written above the line.
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus target="#1b"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4623Prayer">Ṣalot baʾǝnta ḥǝmāma qʷǝrṭat</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ጸሎት፡ በንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ቍርፀት፡ በከፓኮስ፡ 
                        
                           <sic>ስመከ፡</sic>
                         በዳፌል፡ 
                           <sic>ስመከ፡</sic>
                         በኄርያኖስ፡ 
                           <sic>ስመከ፡</sic>
                         በኅቡዕ፡ 
                        
                           <sic>ወበክሠት፡</sic>
                         ስምከ፡ ተማ<supplied reason="omitted">ኅ</supplied>ፀንኩ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        አርጋዔ፡ ነፋሳት፡ ወበረድ፡ ወኃይለ፡ ሰማያት፡ 
                           <sic>ዎምድር፡</sic>
                           <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ወምድር፡</corr>
                         
                        ወኃይለ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ዘአርጋዕከ፡ ከማሆሙ፡ አርግዕ፡ 
                           <sic>ወአቍም፡</sic>
                         
                        
                           <sic>ዝንቱ፡</sic>
                         
                        
                           <sic>ቍርፀት፡</sic>
                         
                        ላዕለ፡ ዓመ<add place="interlinear">ት</add>ከ፡ አጻብዓ፡ ድንግል፡ <add place="overstrike">ወለተ፡ ዓቢየ፡ እግዚእ፡ ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡</add>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>
                        The names of later owners of the scroll, <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11701WalattaAE">Walatta ʿAbiya ʾƎgziʾ</persName> and Kidāna Māryām 
                        (possibly the same as <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11698KidanaMa">Kidāna Māryām</persName>), are written over that of <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11702AsabeaDe">ʾAṣābǝʿa Dǝngǝl</persName>. 
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus target="#1b"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4705MagicPr">Ṣalot baʾǝnta ḥǝmāma wǝgʿāt</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ውግዓት፡ አላህ፡ በላህ፡ ወላህ፡ ሰተፎን፡ ከተፎን፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        በከመ፡ አድኃንኮ፡ ለወልደ፡ ኪራስቂ፡ እምሕማመ፡ ውግዓት፡ ከማሁ፡ አድኅና፡ <choice>
                           <sic>ለዓምከ፡</sic>
                           <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ለዓመትከ፡</corr></choice>
                         
                        ወለተ፡ ዓቢየ፡ እግዚእ፡ <add place="overstrike">ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡</add>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>
                        The names of Kidāna Māryām (possibly the same as <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11698KidanaMa">Kidāna Māryām</persName>) is written over that of 
                        <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11702AsabeaDe">ʾAṣābǝʿa Dǝngǝl</persName>. 
                        Few words have been added at the end of the text, to fill an empty space, among which: <q xml:lang="gez">እስክንድሮስ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ዘከመ፡ ሐዘለ፡</q>.
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
          
